This is set of perl tests for test code quality, if all test passes we know that our code:
- have no syntax errors
- have no Windows (R) end of lines and spaces on the end of line
- use strict and warnings
- have no FIXME mark
- have no tabs
- pass kwalitee test for cpan distribution
- has cyclomatic complexity and lines count (in subs) no bigger than set in test
- has valid POD that cover all function (POD pass spellcheck)
- has test that cover needed part of code
